                            <comment id="120936" author="rwinch" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2015 22:27:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks this is now fixed by keeping track of the original SecurityContext and then restoring it. Can you please give the latest 3.2.9.CI-SNAPSHOT or 4.0.3.CI-SNAPSHOT a try to verify it resolves your issue?&lt;/p&gt;

