&lt;p&gt;Instructions for getting 3.2.9.CI-SNAPSHOT can be found at &lt;a href=&quot;http://docs.spring.io/spring-security/site/docs/3.2.x-SNAPSHOT/reference/htmlsingle/#get-spring-security&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://docs.spring.io/spring-security/site/docs/3.2.x-SNAPSHOT/reference/htmlsingle/#get-spring-security&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
